Ann what's the deal for saturday?&nbsp;
Gid zei dat er iets leuks was, dupont ofzo.
Handen omhoog of ik schiet. Dan kunnen we nog eens een liedje aanvragen, speciaal voor ons. All day long...

so perhaps.

Go out more? I really enjoyed saturday-evening and night. It wasn't a real party but a get-together of old friends.&nbsp;
Surprised how good everything was picked up, conversations, teasing, complots, juicy gossipping!&nbsp;

I like the fact we don't have to meet every week to keep liking each other :)&nbsp;

sO im trying to read up on my friends journals. Beware
